---- USER STORY #9----

#9 As a user, I can view a shape report of all shapes sorted by area

  a) Description:
       A user can view shapes without sorting.
       A user can view shapes with sorting by area.
       A user cannot view unshared or rejected shapes when sorting by area.
  b) Tasks:
      As a user, I can view my own shapes and view other users' shapes.
      As a user, I can view shape reports with sorting by area, which sorts all of the shape reports by area.
  c) Tests:
      Verify that users can view shapes online.
      Verify that users can view only approved shapes.
      Verify that users can view shapes by area.
      Verify that users can only view approved shapes when sorting by area.
  d) Assignee:
       ??
  e) Estimation: ??
  f) Priority: ??
  g) Done:
      All shapes are displayed correctly.
      All shapes can be sorted by area and viewed only if approved by an administrator.
      Only approved shapes can be viewed regardless of what the shapes are being sorted by.
